  ## Installation
For this project I installed Node.js <br> Npm <br> Inquirer<br> Package.json <br> Express <br> MySQL2 <br> console.tablepackage

## Usage
This application is the blue print for a content management systems (CMS) for a small size company. It is meant to be used my a company to keep track of their employees in different departments; their roles, names and other imprtant information that is needed.

